<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="449">l.c.</emphasis>
) disagreed, using the name in the sense of his designated type material in LINN (and 
<taxonomicName authority="Michx." authorityName="Michx." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Cornaceae" genus="Cornus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="stolonifera">
